Attend weekly meeting with both hotels GM to review any feedback, give new ideas on improving the sales of the cards, in increasing the use of the cards in the hotels outlets as well as any operation problems or suggestion that need to be solved. Look out for new opportunity to open other programme for the company in Indonesia and advised the company accordingly.
